      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software (Ansys Mechanical) holds ISO 9001 certification and FDA-recognized validation documentation; version control and change management procedures are documented.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is a commercially validated finite element solver with documented QA procedures conforming to ISO 9001. Software version control logs and release notes were reviewed; no anomalies were identified. Achieved level meets required level."
    },
    {
