      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems with known analytical solutions are solved and results compared; errors within 1% of analytical solution.",
      "rationale": "Standard beam bending and contact patch benchmark cases were executed. FEA results agreed with analytical solutions to within 0.4%, confirming code correctness for the relevant physics. Achieved level meets required level."
